CLASS:: FoaMirror
summary:: First Order Ambisonic (FOA) mirror transformer from the Ambisonic Toolkit (ATK)
categories:: Ambisonic Toolkit, UGens>Multichannel>Ambisonics, UGens>Multichannel>Panners
related:: Classes/FoaTransform, Classes/FoaXform, Reference/SomeRelatedStuff, etc.

DESCRIPTION::
Mirror a first order ambisonic signal (B-format) across an arbitrary plane. link::Classes/FoaMirror:: is usually called via the convenience wrapper link::Classes/FoaTransform::.


NOTE::
Part of the Ambisonic Toolkit, a soundfield kernel synthesis, processing and rendering library.

